screen_desc:
The screenshot shows a ride reservation interface with the title "Reserve a ride." The starting location is "Washington Hilton," and the destination is "Virginia Hospital Center." Below the destination input, there are several location options listed:

1. Virginia Hospital Center, 1701 N George Mason Dr, Arlington, VA
2. Virginia Hospital Center Emergency..., 1701 N George Mason Dr, Arlington, VA
3. VHC Health-Virginia Hospital Center, 1701 N George Mason Dr, Arlington, VA
4. The Virginia Hospital Center, 764 S 23rd St, Arlington, VA
5. VHC Health Outpatient Pavillion, 1851 N George Mason Dr, Arlington, VA

There are also options to "Get more results for VHC Health" and "Set location on map." The top of the screen shows the time (8:55 AM) and various status icons, including battery, signal strength, and notifications.
